StatementHelp.#cdata:
Syntax: REPEATED SUBJECT= subject-effect </ options> ; 

The REPEATED statement specifies the correlation structure of the responses for GEE model fitting. In addition, 
the REPEATED statement controls the iterative fitting algorithm and specifies optional output.
